track_notes: At least if you come in this area, you will have 3 summits not far! It is a must and i love those places! hight mountains, take care.
this path has a part very sloopy, you need to be a good climber! may be easier than what it looks.

since we have walked in this area, we know every inches of the ridges. the best way to activate this 3 sota coming from the Seignus by car on a forest road (you can ride bicycle and make the path shorter), is to climb first Mourre Gros, then Caduc to finish by Sangraure. There is no difficulty, just some part where you must be prudent and focused. As it is a long trip, you must be sure the wx is fine and that you get enought water.
